{"tid":1575912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發！！！］岳義士下午2時半東裁提堂！！！","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T05:59:44.000Z","uid":6181,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab44d0929c9527d644a2a5b80905b829ac3be24","tid":1575912,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"【岳義士下午2時半東裁提堂】<br />\n<br />\n周日晚在炮台山因救人而不幸被捕，更在電視台鏡頭前，被黑警打至頭破血流及在傷口被噴射胡椒噴劑的岳義士，今日 (9月17日) 下午2時30分在東區裁判法院提堂，有關控罪及庭號正待警方通知。<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟懇請各同道下午到庭聲援，以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2548712702082513&amp;id=1965117443775378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2548712702082513%26id%3D1965117443775378&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=1a4690d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2548712702082513&amp;id=1965117443775378</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/sparkalliancehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsparkalliancehk&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=b1eae18c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sparkalliancehk</a>"},{"pid":"30d32e72fccf4747ae8b5f564de1d3353b32fb98","tid":1575912,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuvNTvs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuvNTvs.jpg&h=69affe30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a0c38bd1ab2ed051e6f82b54388b69e17b26477","tid":1575912,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrP